Class AbstractCapitalEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
      • com.poesys.accounting.db.account.AbstractCapitalEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICapitalEntity, com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CapitalEntity

    public abstract class AbstractCapitalEntity
extends com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
implements ICapitalEntity

    A data-access layer data-transfer object for the CapitalEntity. This class is an abstract class that contains AndroMDA generated code; change nothing in this class. Instead, override any methods in the concrete subclass generated in the same package. AndroMDA will overwrite this class each time you run it but will never overwrite the concrete subclass.

    Stereotypes:

    • NaturalKey
    • Persistent

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
